خِطّة (خِطَط)%plan% 19* % Or "project, projected course". Also pronounced خُطَّة‎. From the root خ ط ط‎ (ḵ-ṭ-ṭ). Compare خَطَّ • (ḵaṭṭa) I, non-past يَخُطُّ‎ (yaḵuṭṭu) "to draw a line; to carve, inscribe". Different from root ق ط ع "Related to cut and separate".
حَضَر / يَحْضُر%to attend% 19* % From the root ح ض ر‎ (ḥ-ḍ-r), "related to being present". Compare "lecture" (مُحاضَرة) from Unit 18, "certainly" (حاضِر) from Unit 11.
